    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted as a complete record of the COU2 evaluation. All 13 credibility factors have been addressed (7 assessed, 6 not-assessed as epistemic gaps). The primary credibility claim documents the team's overall finding that the model does not meet MRL 5 requirements; evidence from mesh-refinement and experimental hemolysis studies was reviewed and informed this finding. The package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier with the explicit decision that the model itself is Not Accepted for the intended use.",
